'''中國－湯加關係'''（{{lang-en|China–Tonga relations}}）是指中國和湯加之間的關係。兩國于1998年建交，双方在外交、经济和军事上维持了较为密切的关系。

==背景==
:{{seealso|中国－大洋洲关系}}
对中华人民共和国和[[中华民国|中华民国]]（[[台湾|台湾]]）来说，大洋洲是开展外交竞争的重要地区。大洋洲有8个国家或地区承认中华人民共和国，有6个国家或地区承认中华民国，这两个数字常因大洋洲的岛国在承认[[北京|北京]]和[[台北|台北]]政权的摇摆而改变。由于[[一个中国|一个中国]]的政策，不可能有国家同时与中华人民共和国和中华民国保持外交关系，因而中华人民共和国和中华民国都对大洋洲的小岛国加以外交恩惠以获取外交承认。<ref name="radioaustralia.net.au">[http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/news/infocus/s1842245.htm "The Pacific Proxy: China vs Taiwan"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/news/infocus/s1842245.htm |date=20071104024039 }}, Graeme Dobell, ABC Radio Australia, February 7, 2007</ref><ref name="NZ_Herald_10470950">{{cite news |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/democracy/news/article.cfm?c_id=171&objectid=10470950 |title=Chequebooks brought out at Pacific forum |author=Young, Audrey |date=October 19, 2007 |work=[[The_New_Zealand_Herald|The New Zealand Herald]] |accessdate=November 2, 2011 |archive-date=2013-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208114447/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/democracy/news/article.cfm?c_id=171&objectid=10470950 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2003年，中华人民共和国宣布其将加大与[[太平洋岛国论坛|太平洋岛国论坛]]的外交联系，并加大对该组织的经济援助。<ref>[http://pg.china-embassy.org/eng/zbgx/t46835.htm "China announces initiatives to expand ties with PIF member countries"] {{Wayback|url=http://pg.china-embassy.org/eng/zbgx/t46835.htm |date=20170819190012 }}, PRC embassy in Papua New Guinea, November 24, 2003</ref> 2006年，中国总理[[温家宝|温家宝]]宣称将加大中国同太平洋岛国之间的经济合作，中国将提供更多的经济援助，免除最不发达国家出口到中国商品的关税，减免这些国家的债务，捐助抗疟疾药物，并提供对2000名岛国的官员和技术人员的培训。<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2006-04/05/content_560910.htm "China offers aid package to Pacific Islands"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2006-04/05/content_560910.htm |date=20121006175713 }}, ''China Daily'', April 5, 2006</ref> 2006年，温家宝成为第一位访问太平洋岛国的中国总理。[[南太平洋大学|南太平洋大学]]的太平洋研究专家Ron Crocombe教授指出，“相比其它国家，有更多的太平洋岛国官员前往中国进行访问”。<ref>[http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2006/04/03/2003300678 "Chinese Premier Wen to visit the Pacific Islands"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2006/04/03/2003300678 |date=20120912133356 }}, ''Taipei Times'', April 3, 2006</ref>

==汤加华人现状==
截至2001年，大约有三千至四千[[海外華人|华人]]居住在汤加，占总人口的3%至4%。<ref name="NZ_Herald_229612">{{cite news |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=229612 |title=Editorial: Racist moves will rebound on Tonga |date=November 23, 2001 |work=[[The_New_Zealand_Herald|The New Zealand Herald]] |accessdate=November 2, 2011 |archive-date=2014-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015061422/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=229612 |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[汤加华人|汤加华人]]是汤加主要的少数民族族群，自二十世纪九十年代起遭受了包括种族暴力在内的显著的种族歧视。<ref name="NZ_Herald_141510">{{cite news |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/world/news/article.cfm?c_id=2&objectid=141510 |title=Tonga's Prince takes swipe at racism at home and abroad |date=June 26, 2000 |work=[[The_New_Zealand_Herald|The New Zealand Herald]] |accessdate=November 2, 2011 |archive-date=2011-08-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60rMW1U1k?url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/world/news/article.cfm?c_id=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NZ_Herald_229521">{{cite news |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/world/news/article.cfm?c_id=2&objectid=229521 |title=Tonga to expel race-hate victims |author=Paul Raffaele and Mathew Dearnaley |date=November 22, 2001 |work=[[The_New_Zealand_Herald|The New Zealand Herald]] |accessdate=November 2, 2011 |archive-date=2011-08-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60rMBDqWp?url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/world/news/article.cfm?c_id=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2006年，[[2006年努库阿洛法骚乱|骚乱者]]严重捣毁了汤加华人在[[努库阿洛法|努库阿洛法]]所开的商店。<ref name="radioaustralia.net.au"/><ref>[http://english.people.com.cn/200611/17/eng20061117_322437.html "Chinese stores looted in Tonga riots"] {{Wayback|url=http://english.people.com.cn/200611/17/eng20061117_322437.html |date=20130512170138 }}, ''People's Daily'', November 17, 2006</ref>

这些事件对中国－汤加关系并没有显著的负面影响。2011年，汤加外交副部长对中国持续的经济援助回应说“我们同中国有着密切的双边关系”。<ref>[http://www.taimionline.com/articles/2811 "Roads reconstructed with China loan"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.taimionline.com/articles/2811 |date=20110324135707 }}, Taimi Media Network, March 15, 2011</ref>

==当前关系==
汤加自1998年起一直承认中华人民共和国。

2001年，汤加同中国宣布加强双方的军事关系。<ref>[http://en.people.cn/english/200105/15/eng20010515_70060.html "China, Tonga Vow to Further Military Ties"] {{Wayback|url=http://english.peopledaily.com.cn/english/200105/15/eng20010515_70060.html|date=20130609041409}}, ''People's Daily'', May 15, 2001</ref> 2008年，中国对汤加提供了超过34万欧元的军事设备。<ref>"Chinese Government Donates Military Supplies to TDS", Tonga Now, January 9, 2008</ref>

2006年，在努库阿洛法骚乱之后，[[中国进出口银行|中国进出口银行]]对汤加提供了利率只有2%的1亿1800万美元贷款，其中的大部分用于支付给中国公司开展的基础建设。<ref name=Age2014>{{cite news|last1=Perry|first1=Nick|title=How China's gift of an aeroplane put Tonga, New Zealand at odds.|url=http://www.theage.com.au/world/how-chinas-gift-of-an-aeroplane-put-tonga-new-zealand-at-odds-20140625-zskxb.html|accessdate=25 June 2014|work=The Age|publisher=Fairfax|date=25 June 2014|archive-date=2014-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140914083242/http://www.theage.com.au/world/how-chinas-gift-of-an-aeroplane-put-tonga-new-zealand-at-odds-20140625-zskxb.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2008年4月，汤加国王[[乔治·图普五世|乔治·图普五世]]访问中国，重申对一个中国政策的支持。根据[[新华社|新华社]]的报道，国王表示支持中国政府在[[2008年西藏骚乱|西藏骚乱]]中所采取的措施。<ref>[http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-04/10/content_7954657.htm "Tonga supports China's stance on Taiwan, Tibet"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-04/10/content_7954657.htm |date=20121014071057 }}, Xinhua, April 10, 2008</ref> 国王会见中国国防部部长[[梁光烈|梁光烈]]，以加强双方在军事上的交流同合作。<ref>[http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-04/15/content_7981846.htm "Chinese Defense Minister meets Tongan King"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-04/15/content_7981846.htm |date=20121016060355 }}, Xinhua, April 15, 2008</ref>

2013年，中国政府赠送了60架[[新舟60|新舟60]]给汤加的航空公司。<ref name=Age2014/><ref>{{cite news|last1=Arrow|first1=Brendan|title=Tonga loses NZ aid over use of suspect Chinese aircraft|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-07-09/an-tonga-loses-nz-aid-over-use-of-suspect-chinese-aircraft/4809676|accessdate=25 June 2014|work=Australia News Network|date=10 July 2013|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305040042/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-07-09/an-tonga-loses-nz-aid-over-use-of-suspect-chinese-aircraft/4809676|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年6月，中国同汤加签订了两国之间的《关于互免普通护照人员签证的协定》，并于同年8月19日生效。

